Yes, Unitron is a Newcomer, but Prowl isn't a Predacon, Inferno.

::Prowl/Zeus::

Prowl grins at Lunarpine, "No can do, you're getting in a CR chamber whether 
you like it or n-"

Shots from Unitron dig into the base of his wing, sending Prowl crashing down 
to the ground. Prowl sits up, firing an acid pellet at Unitron.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Zeus opens his eyes. He was in severe pain, complete with nearly-critical 
damage done to his systems from the crash. He crawls slowly toward Shuko.

"Sir," he coughs out, "I suggest we make a tactical withdrawl. Without Ra, we 
cannot form Dark Messiah."
